            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/475.html" rel="bookmark">[ Lumen 5.1 文档 ] 更多特性 —— Session</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-08-22T12:42:16+08:00">2015-08-22</time>
